---
import { ArrowRight } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section
  class="relative h-[70vh] min-h-[500px] w-full overflow-hidden bg-safari-900 text-white"
  aria-label="The Great Migration"
>
  <!-- Video background -->
  <video
    autoplay
    muted
    loop
    playsinline
    preload="metadata"
    poster="https://res.cloudinary.com/wqmnkfgf/image/upload/v1783581264/migration-poster_alxkbn.jpg"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover scale-105 ken-burns"
  >
    <source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/wqmnkfgf/video/upload/v1783581312/migration-mobile_vsmytk.mp4" type="video/mp4" media="(max-width: 768px)" />
    <source src="https://res.cloudinary.com/wqmnkfgf/video/upload/v1783581333/migration-desktop_eeu7pv.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
  </video>

  <!-- Two stacked gradients for legibility -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-black/85 via-black/45 to-black/20"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-transparent to-black/40"></div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="container-content relative z-10 h-full flex flex-col justify-end pb-16 md:pb-20 pt-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl reveal-up">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="h-px w-10 md:w-14 bg-savannah-500"></span>
        <p class="eyebrow text-savannah-300 text-[11px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em]">
          The Great Migration
        </p>
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-[2.6rem] sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl font-medium tracking-tight text-white mb-5 md:mb-6 leading-[1.05]" style="text-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.35)">
        Two million animals.<br />
        <span class="italic font-normal text-savannah-300">One timeless journey.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-dusk-100/90 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-light mb-8" style="text-shadow: 0 1px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)">
        Every year, over two million wildebeest, zebra, and gazelle thunder across the Serengeti–Maasai Mara ecosystem in the largest mammal migration on Earth. Witness it from the front row.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/plan-my-trip" class="btn btn-primary px-7 py-3.5">
          Plan your migration safari
          <ArrowRight size={16} />
        </a>
        <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-outline-light px-7 py-3.5 border-white/30 hover:bg-white hover:text-safari-900">
          Migration guide
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ken-burns {
    animation: ken-burns 24s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  @keyframes ken-burns {
    from { transform: scale(1.05); }
    to { transform: scale(1.18); }
  }

  .reveal-up {
    animation: reveal-up 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) 0.15s both;
  }
  @keyframes reveal-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ken-burns { animation: none; }
    .reveal-up { animation: none; }
  }
</style>
